body_html:
Worked great!

On Mon, May 23, 2016, 7:57 PM cg31 notifications@github.com wrote:

I got the same error today. It seems protobuf is messed up.

I fixed it by cleaning and updating it:

git submodule foreach git clean -dfx
git submodule update

—
